    rdfs:comment "Dui: two Yang below one Yin — complementary to Gen. Where Gen concentrates at the summit, Dui opens at the summit. The lake's surface is open and reflective above solid banks. Archetype of joyful expression, communication, the pleasure of exchange." ;
